<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tang gamla tak achun Kross melsie tak a ding,
 Thawkna leh zahhuoi taklat na;
 Ka ngainai zie Kross chuh mi mangthaite dinga,
 Ngaihum pen leh phapen thihna.

[V2]
 Kross melsie tak chuh ken ka ngainai,
 Ka gallak haw ka ngak masieh in;
 Kross melsie tak chuh tuzing ingka,
 Nikhat tei Lallukhuk then na'ng ka.

[V3]
 2. Aw Zie Kross melsie khawvel mite muhsit chuh,
 Kei vang lunglai ei kuoipen hi;
 Pathien Belam No chun van lopina nusie'n,
 Kalvari tieng pu di'n A hung.

[V4]
 3. Zie Kross melsie Pathien thisan behna achun,
 Hawihna maktak chuh ken ka mui;
 Zie Kross chuh ahi Isu thawkna leh thihna,
 Ei ngaidama, ei hihthieng ding.

[V5]
 4. Kross melsie a ding chun ginum in umzing ka,
 A zahhuoina kipaka puo'n;
 Ei hun sam intin gamla taka ka In ah,
 A lopina chanpih ta'ng ka.</lyrics>
<title>THE OLD RUGGED CROSS</title>
<hymn_number>446</hymn_number>
</song>